{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","subTitleText":"","presenterText":"","dateText":"","logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","smallerSectionText":""},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"text","span":3,"markdown":"Outpatient and OPD curative visits declined sharply after late 2024, falling by about 30% from peaks of ~110,000 (outpatient) and ~95,000 (curative) to lows of ~74,000 and ~64,000, respectively.

A pronounced drop in late 2024 affected all services simultaneously, including follow-up visits.

